92
00:09:24,395 --> 00:09:28,395
<i>to do what Asian boys ought
to be doing for themselves.</i>

93
00:09:28,513 --> 00:09:30,919
President Johnson chose to
reaffirm the Kennedy policy's

94
00:09:30,944 --> 00:09:34,325
