00:13:50,821 --> 00:13:52,727
-Haldeman rang.
-Yeah?

175
00:13:52,830 --> 00:13:55,049
It seems the President
has decided

176
00:13:55,089 --> 00:13:57,460
not to provide Judith
with credentials

