-I know.

182
00:14:06,881 --> 00:14:08,360
-I know, but don't...
-Jesus.

183
00:14:08,431 --> 00:14:09,134
But what?

184
00:14:09,159 --> 00:14:11,208
I'm not sure I entirely
blame the President

185
00:14:11,233 --> 00:14:12,759
-on this one, Dan.
-No?

186
00:14:12,849 --> 00:14:15,318
