she crashed Julie's reception.

189
00:14:20,419 --> 00:14:22,387
-They're being punitive.
-Her pen is so sharp.

190
00:14:22,412 --> 00:14:23,662
-Of course it's punitive.
-This is punitive.

191
00:14:23,717 --> 00:14:24,857
Of course it's punitive.

192
00:14:26,118 --> 00:14:30,063
