to a vanilla ice cream cone.

193
00:14:30,118 --> 00:14:32,064
-She did, yeah.
-Yeah.

194
00:14:32,456 --> 00:14:34,253
I mean, why would
her father want Judy

195
00:14:34,278 --> 00:14:35,769
to cover his
daughter's wedding?

196
